# Astro Project Guidelines

## Project Structure
The project follows Astro's recommended structure:
- `src/pages/` - Contains all routes and pages
- `src/components/` - Reusable components
- `src/layouts/` - Page layouts and templates
- `src/styles/` - Global styles and Tailwind configuration
- `public/` - Static assets

## Component Guidelines
- Use `.astro` files for Astro components
- Use `.tsx` for React components only when necessary
- Keep components small and focused
- Use composition over inheritance
- Prefer shadcn-ui components for UI elements

## Styling Guidelines
- Use Tailwind CSS for styling
- Follow mobile-first responsive design
- Use shadcn-ui components for UI elements
- Maintain consistent spacing using Tailwind's spacing scale

## Performance Guidelines
- Use Astro's built-in image optimization
- Implement lazy loading for images below the fold
- Minimize JavaScript usage
- Prefer static generation when possible

## Dependency Management
- Minimize new package additions
- Prefer built-in Astro features
- Use shadcn-ui for UI components
- Keep dependencies up to date

## Accessibility Requirements
- Use semantic HTML elements
- Include proper ARIA attributes
- Ensure proper color contrast
- Make all interactive elements keyboard accessible

## SEO Best Practices
- Use proper meta tags
- Implement structured data when applicable
- Ensure proper heading hierarchy
- Use descriptive alt text for images

## Asset Management
- Store images in `public/` or `src/assets/`
- Use appropriate image formats
- Optimize assets before deployment
- Follow consistent naming conventions

# Astro Project Structure

The main entry point is [src/pages/index.astro](mdc:src/pages/index.astro), which serves as the homepage.

Key directories:
- [src/pages/](mdc:src/pages) - Contains all routes and pages
- [src/components/](mdc:src/components) - Reusable components
- [src/layouts/](mdc:src/layouts) - Page layouts and templates
- [src/styles/](mdc:src/styles) - Global styles and Tailwind configuration
- [public/](mdc:public) - Static assets

The project uses [astro.config.mjs](mdc:astro.config.mjs) for Astro configuration and [tailwind.config.js](mdc:tailwind.config.js) for Tailwind CSS settings.

For UI components, we use shadcn-ui which are located in [src/components/ui/](mdc:src/components/ui).



